value.0: Welcome to D20 Modern.  This conversation ONLY HAPPENS ONCE PER CHARACTER, so keep reading.  Because of NWN's limits on character creation, you may have an alignment you don't want.  This will let you change that.  What alignment would you like?
Done.  Are you satisfied with your alignment choice?

Now, you need to pick a starting occupation.  A hero may hold other jobs as his or her career unfolds, but the benefits of a starting occupation are only applied once, at the time of character creation.

Each occupation provides competence bonuses for 1-3 relevant skills and some starting occupations provide a reputation bonus or a bonus feat. Note that a character still must meet any prerequisites for additional feats, e.g. to obtain medium armour the light armour bonus feat granted by an occupation cannot be used and it must be taken as full feat first.

Finally, a starting occupation increases the character's Wealth bonus.

Now, which occupation would you like?
Done.  You have received the occupation as a feat.  Please check the description on your character sheet and make sure you like what you chose.  Are you satisfied with your occupation choice?
You're all done.  Enjoy D20 Modern!
Because you're human, you can switch to a different character head.  Would you like to try one?
You're all done.  Enjoy D20 Modern!
No - please go back to my original head.
No - please go forward one head.
No - please go back one head.
No - I'd like to try another head.
